P.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025?
P.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

cons_P.title: Will a fictional character be US president in 2025?
cons_P.body: Resolves YES if a fictional character becomes US president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.
